Berikut langkah lengkap menambahkan PWA ke app kamu:

---

## Langkah 1 — Buat file `manifest.json`

Buat file baru bernama `manifest.json` di folder yang sama dengan `index.html`:

```json
{
  "name": "Latihan SKD CPNS",
  "short_name": "SKD CPNS",
  "description": "Aplikasi latihan soal SKD CPNS - TWK, TIU, TKP",
  "start_url": "./index.html",
  "display": "standalone",
  "orientation": "portrait",
  "theme_color": "#1565C0",
  "background_color": "#F0F4FF",
  "lang": "id",
  "icons": [
    {
      "src": "icon-192.png",
      "sizes": "192x192",
      "type": "image/png",
      "purpose": "any maskable"
    },
    {
      "src": "icon-512.png",
      "sizes": "512x512",
      "type": "image/png",
      "purpose": "any maskable"
    }
  ]
}
```

